Text: Thank you so much, I feel so much better reading this

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: Honestly 99% of people don’t pay attention to their  surroundings. She might have read it but   a) instantly forgot it,   b) having no context for it would have no reason to remember it or think on it   c) looked and was probably just as nervous as you because that’s human   D) read it but probably has no idea what is really means   The only reason it would stick out to someone would be if they where in a similar boat and then I can’t see why someone would bring it up or judge
